def cleaner1 (s):
    return s.split('</li>')

def cleaner2 (s): 
    m=  s.replace('<ul>\n<li class="ccl"><strong>', '')
    n = m.replace ('</strong>', '')
    o = n.replace ('n<li class="ccl">', '')
    p = o.replace ('\n<li class = "ccl"><strong>', '')
    q = p.replace ('<ul>\n<li class="ccl">', '')
    r = q.replace ('\n<li class="ccl">', '')
    v = r.replace ('<strong>', '')
    return v

def cleaner3 (list): 
    return [cleaner2(x) for x in list]

def getauthors (string): 
    return re.findall (r'^[^\(]+', string)
da ['authors'] = da['ref'].apply(getauthors)

def gettitle (string):
    return re.findall (r'\)\.(.*?)(?=\.)', string)
da ['article title'] = da ['ref'].apply(gettitle)
